<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/519418-i-am-trying-to-find-good-read-aloud">I am trying to find good read aloud stories for high school students (ages 16-21). I&#39;m trying to read adult/teen books, but need somewhat simple language. The students are from pre-K to 2nd grade in reading level. I love the story &amp; graphics in this book. 

Does this seem like a good match?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_519418'><a id="like_count_community_question_519418" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/519418?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F62005.A_Night_in_the_Lonesome_October">like</a></span>

