<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Snuff (dog)- Jack (the Ripper)<br/>Quicklime (snake) - Rastov (Raputin)<br/>Graymalk (cat)- Crazy Jill (Witch)<br/>Bubo (rat)- The Good Doctor (Victor Frankenstein)<br/>N<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Snuff (dog)- Jack (the Ripper)<br />Quicklime (snake) - Rastov (Raputin)<br />Graymalk (cat)- Crazy Jill (Witch)<br />Bubo (rat)- The Good Doctor (Victor Frankenstein)<br />Needle (bat)- The Count (Dracula)<br />Nightwind (owl) - Morris and McCab<br />Cheeter (squirrel) - Druid Owen<br />Tekela (white raven) - Vicar Roberts<br /><br />Others:<br />The Great Detective (Sherlock) and "Companion" (Watson)<br />Larry Talbot (Wolf man, has plants)<br /><br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
