              <span id="reviewTextContainer210147560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4614604593569777792">This books holds a special place in my heart, as it is the one book he shared with me as he wrote it. One of the best times I ever had with my father. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

